{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"traditional\"><p id=\"a20d224c568e48b9d67847a2c66a8c01_p_0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29); background-color: #FCFCCA; font-size: 15px\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FCFCCA; font-size: 15px\">语雀反馈通道</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"background-color: #FCFCCA; font-size: 15px\">， 感谢你的支持！</span></p><h2 id=\"JZSuD\"></h2><h2 id=\"e11d9bba\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如何使用</span></h2><p id=\"4838965d80065e01b01bcecbc05930c6_p_1\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"6338fe661d6617aef22bcfcc9aa8cfc7_p_2\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">你可以在工具栏的第一个绿色按钮「插入卡片」中找到插入公式等入口。随后在公式编辑区域输入 LaTeX 语法即可实时预览。</span></p><p id=\"804b58e6d41ad7fb2480630c3092516e_p_3\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"72463c7b18450670c3a6f51a033e7705_p_4\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634187818778-0095c278-ab0b-4988-aac8-42e06735278b.png\" width=\"960\" id=\"u5eda485f\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"7467903a77e4c43e92d4f196903d0bbe_p_5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"f23fb9c519ff30bfe03d0b2cc2cac85d_p_6\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"6505e4272d346fab0c27c5fcfc256830_p_7\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">同时支持以下快捷键（</span><span class=\"ne-text\">支持中文，拼音和英文别名</span><span class=\"ne-text\">）</span></p><p id=\"11549833f10d5230edce160de487a1ff_p_8\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/公式</span></code></p><p id=\"75891707bb48e0fc6f9d301763f39865_p_9\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/gongshi</span></code></p><p id=\"e563d6cd041306d58ce9897e2a61b163_p_10\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/formula</span></code></p><p id=\"828bea0262f636b25c97fbef525aed20_p_11\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"09a2b5671cf447a1a3529d71c89cf9e1_p_12\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"b5be0d49bc4c6693f350ee28d5ee5ece_p_13\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">例如我在输入框输入下面代码：</span></p><p id=\"7cf79ceeaaf91ef14264b4c55c1c8c1d_p_14\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><pre data-language=\"plain\" id=\"QqXrS\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-plain\">\\sum_{i=0}^n i^2 = \\frac{(n^2+n)(2n+1)}{6}</pre><p id=\"c53070088aadb43ef468f61fca8ca22a_p_15\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"89149757fe09db496815bceff34d13e9_p_16\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">即可以看到公式内容为：</span><span id=\"jc4W3\" class=\"ne-math\"><img src=\"https://cdn.yuque.com/__latex/7871fbdd01f5f3d83f6f52968e565f35.svg\"></span></p><p id=\"c5eaf555cee01ec836fc749258c6179d_p_17\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"f4864a86\"><span class=\"ne-text\">样式布局和对齐方式</span></h2><p id=\"3f8949dd5527f0c9624c3fd3faefb76f_p_18\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u76f18f93\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">升级后的公式支持颜色调整和字号调整，也支持设置成标题。</span></p><p id=\"u1a1b74b9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"d22e1b32b0c52c70f327ca414b08425f_p_19\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">公式支持行内模式和块级模式。行内模式将会嵌入到文本中，被文本内容环绕；块级模式将会是独占一行，不会有文本环绕，会有留白。</span></p><p id=\"db841a6e995b001085603629a3ace379_p_20\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"4cecac1a46f26a99c9ba7fdfd3fdd5c8_p_21\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">只有在块级模式下才支持对齐方式，目前支持左对齐，居中对齐、右对齐三种方式。</span></p><p id=\"37928cd1f32681ee4810a9ab9d3c1104_p_22\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"2e634146\"><span class=\"ne-text\">更多支持</span></h2><p id=\"4547a4b65fb57fca5301c6973643450c_p_23\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"6210b2cabe5243164298fb44628fe10c_p_24\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">目前采用 </span><a href=\"https://katex.org/\" data-href=\"https://katex.org/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Katex</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\"> 库生成 </span><em><span class=\"ne-text\">LaTeX </span></em><span class=\"ne-text\">数学公式，因此有一个门槛是你需要熟知一点 LaTeX 语法，你可以参考：</span></p><p id=\"3afe72986fc83f6913935faccbcf69b2_p_25\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"78c38cff1cb7e1f14857b68164376f4a_li_0\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/brzicb\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/brzicb\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">数学公式举例</span></a></li><li id=\"ufd769992\"><a href=\"https://katex.org/docs/supported.html\" data-href=\"https://katex.org/docs/supported.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Katex Function</span></a></li><li id=\"1edc1ce38b17cf223a4edba1c485d224_li_1\"><a href=\"http://meta.math.stackexchange.com/questions/5020/mathjax-basic-tutorial-and-quick-reference\" data-href=\"http://meta.math.stackexchange.com/questions/5020/mathjax-basic-tutorial-and-quick-reference\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">LaTex 语法</span></a></li></ul><p id=\"4cc44302cfe9be1836a49b383f7e914f_p_27\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"b20e6ec4\"><span class=\"ne-text\">典型案例</span></h2><p id=\"d17d837b16c49a0e5c21edc18722e410_p_28\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"4b05f98fc51bf9dbee4d822814939040_li_2\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/liujindong/math/px9d6x\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/liujindong/math/px9d6x\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">函数的性质</span></a></li></ul><p id=\"d8f02fc6e1d9d5e68b5ff128662a6b29_p_29\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"58edab18de1c8434bf226aab907be2e9_p_30\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/topics\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/topics\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可以到语雀讨论区进行反馈</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">。感谢你的支持！</span></p></div>",
